headline: American-Made Growth: 4 Top Restaurant Stocks Fueling U.S. Expansion
summary: Quick-service restaurant (QSR) expansion is a great American investment theme.  While not without risks, expansion is one of the biggest growth drivers for quick-service restaurant operators.  There are a number of QSR operators that still have a long runway of expansion ahead.

headline: 3 Companies Boosting U.S. Economic Growth
summary: Coca-Cola is attracting investor enthusiasm because it has reliably generated sales and increased shareholder value.  Chipotle Mexican Grill is going through a rough patch but has plenty of expansion opportunities.  President Donald Trump has been amplifying his tariff program in response to what he says is an imbalance in trade between the U.S., and other countries.
